{
  "stem": "6503.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the German took at lot away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What kind of events?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wrote right away a letter to my sister, who was in the United States.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know she lived in New York.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wrote a letter to my sister.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- and I can show you, I got a telegram back that she was happy that I survived with my husband, and that she was married.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I knew that she was married to Rein already, and that she had the baby.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was the first knowledge that she had that I was survive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was the only one in the family who survived.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I knew that she was there, and she contacted me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She had my address, and she wrote me letters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she started sending me, also, packages from the United States, so I should have something to eat.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was in '45.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She sended me packages, and clothing, and all kind.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Most of the clothing, I couldn't wear, because she didn't know what I needed or whatever.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I gave it away, or I changed it for something else.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the beginning, I-- we didn't work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What we did, we changed with the Canadians.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went out, we tried to get food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The main thing was food, because that was the thing that was the most critical.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in order to get that, we had to-- my husband used to buy from them [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] cigarettes, giving to Dutch people, and then we tried to give them what they wanted, like watches, cameras, if we had, and we changed that for-- for the cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And with the cigarettes, we could get.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was the commodity, the cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "People wanted American cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
